<div class="title">So Crazy</div>
<div class="substance">Alprazolam (Xanax) & Alcohol - Hard</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Lutesium&Exact=1">Lutesium</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Lutesium. "So Crazy: An Experience with Alprazolam (Xanax) & Alcohol - Hard (exp17398)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Apr 1, 2006. erowid.org/exp/17398</div>

<br/>



